Her crimson optics went from Azureblade to Scourge. 

Remaining straight faced & unmoving. then cocking a 'brow'. Save her? Was 
every Male bot simply attracted to her & acting foolish?! 

Then turned her attention again to Azureblade, "What is it that you want of 
me." Glancing at Scourge, "Or are you like this one," indicating to Scourge," 
here to supposedly rescue me?" 

A faint image she remembered of a dragon... a kiss.... her sparked warmed at 
the thought... a face, though blurry & cloudy was seen. One from a long ago 
time.
